name: Steven Junior MABLE, Petitioner v. Stephen P. LINEBAUGH, P.J., Respondent

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 29th day of June, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED, and the Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
